title: Help.
body: So I played the Doom bots the other day and winning that game and I was waiting to get my summoner icon like they said. I played on Oct 18th and yesterday at 5pm EST and still haven't gotten it. Please help me, I just want a teemo summoner icon.

replies.body: We're still sending out the icons to eligible players, and aim it have it finished by the 17th per the [Teemoing ](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/skins/the-teemoing-2016)announcement.  Some players may get them before others.  Hang tight until then!
